Delete an App
You can delete an app if you have Manager access. Deleting an app permanently removes all lenses, dashboards, and datasets.
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.
Open the app, click Delete.
Note: You can't recover a deleted app.
CRM Analytics lists affected lenses and dashboards outside your app. When datasets are deleted, referenced lenses or dashboards become unusable.
Click Delete Asset(s).
